  "text": "However, the molecular mechanisms responsible for such alterations, the contribution of high DLG1 expression to tumour prognosis and the precise temporal deregulation of this protein at different stages of cancer progression are not fully understood. In addition, despite the fact that DLG1 has been postulated as a tumour suppressor some paradoxical data indicate that, under certain conditions, it may have oncogenic activities (Frese et al., 2006; [CITATION_1] .",
